    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Internal Infection\nMental status changes\n,\nheadache\n,\nnausea and vomiting\n, irritability\nNeck stiffness (33% of patients)\nFever\nis often absent\nAbdominal pain\n(VP shunt)\nExternal Infection\nSwelling, erythema, tenderness along site of shunt tubing",
